    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54 platform, meticulously maintained for the discerning purist. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, both of which have been fully overhauled to ensure optimal camshaft timing and throttle response. Critical preventative maintenance is documented, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate chassis fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, delivering power to a pristine limited-slip differential. Finished in collector-grade condition with zero bushing deflection and a factory-spec suspension geometry, this M3 offers the raw, mechanical feedback synonymous with BMW\u2019s golden era.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Original paint. No accidents. Service records included. Interior like new. Inspection ready.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This is a rare, museum-grade example that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or blemishes to be found. Inside, the cabin feels and smells like it just left the showroom; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the original trim is free of any scratches. Every mechanical component has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, resulting in a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and indistinguishable from new. This vehicle comes complete with its full service history, all original keys, and the factory-issued manuals. For the collector seeking a true time capsule, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
