    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible, flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. You've really gotta see this beauty in person to believe it!",
