    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six with factory-spec individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, and the rod bearings were proactively replaced with WPC-treated units. The rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The suspension retains its communicative geometry, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein B16 dampers. Zero fluid seepage, no VANOS rattle, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
